commit.message:
GTIFNewWithMethodsEx: Fix allocation of tempData.

tempData.tk_asciiParams is freed in the failure handler, so tempData
must be allocated before the first `goto failure;`

Found with a GDAL geotiff fuzzer.

Issue introduced in https://github.com/OSGeo/libgeotiff/commit/e98322fe0e4dabec16d428cd397ed7050f5aad7a

```
    if( pszReturn == NULL )
                  ^

```
